Your father is a powerful figure in the music industry.

11
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,280
Your connections are extensive.

12
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:35,920
But I

13
00:01:36,759 --> 00:01:38,440
am content with my current life.

14
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,720
I have a happy family

15
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,539
