21
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,960
Think about it.

22
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,520
Honey.

23
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:14,250
The awards at this art festival seem quite prestigious.

24
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,680
I'm definitely going to win a prize.

25
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,840
You're so confident.

26
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,280
But I believe in your abilities.

27
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,640
By the way,

28
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:29,220
you mentioned you were under a lot of stress.

29
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,880
Can you tell me why?

30
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:36,760
Your daughter is like a bottomless pit

31
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:39,680
that will drain all your savings.

32
